reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great bag for the price
reviews.reviewText: This is a really good and sturdy bag. It's not heavy or light, durable enough for the gym. Haven't used it on any flights but I'm very positive that it will survive multiple flights plus daily activity. It is big enough for a weekender, big enough for gym clothes, gym accessories and your toiletries. It does stand upright, while empty, when set on the ground. It will not fold upon itself. For 25 dollars it's a perfect bag.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great weekend or gym bag.
reviews.reviewText: Love this bag! The price is great. Perfect size for a weekend travel or a gym bag. Lots of inside pockets and zippered outside pockets. It has nice padded handles and an attachable shoulder strap. The canvas like material is durable and easy to clean. It would also make great gift. I highly recommend purchasing this bag.
